text: Juan Amalio Paladino Jaunsolo was a foil and sabre fencer from Uruguay. Paladino competed at the 1948 and 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born on 17 February 1925.Juan Paladino == References == Category:1925 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Fencers Category:Olympians for Uruguay Category:Sportspeople from Montevideo
